				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/B%E1%BB%91c-to%C3%A1n-t%E1%BB%AD-Phong-v%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%91ng-xu%C3%A2n-quy/poem-KJV6EkjcMLmQRYkXLQh-xw">Bốc toán tử (Phong vũ tống xuân quy) - 卜算子（風雨送春歸）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/author-FbbINXH7lzqgF9ytJv8P4Q">Thái Thân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Ch%C3%BA/Chu-trung-ng%E1%BA%ABu-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-mhNx9UO2oRnWKdKClEVguQ">Chu trung ngẫu vịnh - 舟中偶詠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Ch%C3%BA/author-rkS7BX3Bcpb1lFiLF2a3rw">Phan Huy Chú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-%C4%90%C4%A9nh/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-ti%E1%BB%85n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-ki%C3%AAm-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa/poem-T65vF1q6I6UY3hUEAvQ49g">Đồng tiễn Dương tướng quân kiêm Nguyên Châu đô đốc ngự sử trung thừa - 同餞陽將軍兼源州都督御史中丞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-%C4%90%C4%A9nh/author-0TWvSc_szNjkT3qt3VdtPw">Tô Đĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0n-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-KVqBR2JrNTFyC6LenDt99g">Hoạ Nguỵ bộc xạ hoàn hương - 和魏僕射還鄉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/author-AKTNQoEgmd-YADK1_8RKQg">Trương Duyệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Li%E1%BB%87t-n%E1%BB%AF-L%C3%BD-Tam-h%C3%A0nh/poem-kAXSQG8h5bUMBdRjj9Vfhg">Liệt nữ Lý Tam hành - 烈女李三行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99ng-L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-ToSLk0xVwCUYLAgn3x6WdQ">Mộng Lý Bạch kỳ 2 - 夢李白其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Ng%E1%BB%A5-c%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-Tu%E1%BB%87-vi%E1%BB%87n-chi-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-t%E1%BA%A1p-hoa-m%C3%A3n-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BB%AFu-h%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-w99oAsfudXJjoGO0C6_FbA">Ngụ cư Định Tuệ viện chi đông tạp hoa mãn sơn hữu hải đường - 寓居定慧院之東雜花滿山有海棠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Song-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t/poem-ZsTekGVIqDbk5P8n4WFENg">Song thập nhất - 雙十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nguy%C3%AAn-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-IuY5ty-lKqSV9eUw78nM9Q">Thượng nguyên ứng chế - 上元應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/author-IRXLchCCp9FCax7d5XFTCQ">Vương Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-H%E1%BB%93ng-B%C3%A0ng-k%E1%BB%B7/poem-fnfV2OF34VftNTPstCykCA">Vịnh sử Hồng Bàng kỷ - 詠史鴻龐紀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
